OK, so I've done a quick reading of this series (I usually don't read yuri doujins but I gave this one a try) and this is what I have to say (IMO): art is mediocre, but the story is decent, I enjoyed it, a coming-of-age type of love story where teenage girls explore their feelings. I recommend this if you are into yuri.
